des: WMHB is a student-run non-commercial radio station operating year-round out of Colby College. The station features a wide variety of programming, including podcasts, interviews, talk shows, live event broadcasts, and an eclectic mix of music. Members of the Waterville community, as well as students and faculty members broadcast on WMHB throughout the year.
